These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: mirinda, fanta, soy-milk, iced-tea, sprite
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: superhero, adventure, disaster, time-travel, musical
There are 5 different nationalities: japanese, nigerian, pakistani, indian, spanish
5 different pets are kept: dog, frog, horse, cat, turtle
 1. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
 2. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 3. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
 4. the person drinking soy-milk is the person drinking soy-milk##1
 5. the owner of the dog is the person watching superhero movies##1
 6. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 7. the japanese is on the left of the pakistani##1
 8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 9. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
11. the person drinking sprite is between the nigerian and the person watching musical movies##2
12. the indian is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
13. the spanish is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Beverage      | mirinda        | fanta | sprite     | soy-milk   | iced-tea |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster     | adventure      | time-travel | musical   | superhero    |
| Nationality   | indian  | nigerian     | japanese | pakistani | spanish  |
| Pet           | frog | horse      | turtle     | cat   | dog     |

