.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: baking, magic-tricks, puzzles, board-games, sudoku
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: jazz, house, ambient, funk, classical
There are 5 different nationalities: british, nigerian, canadian, german, indonesian
The people use 5 different means of transport: jet-ski, boat, ship, airplane, snowmobile
 1. the person driving the snowmobile is in the middle##1
 2. the fan of classical is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the nigerian##1
 5. the person driving the boat is between the british and the fan of classical##2
 6. the person driving the airplane is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 7. the fan of jazz is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 8. the canadian is the fan of funk##1
 9. the canadian is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
10. the fan of ambient is on the right of the fan of house##1
11. the canadian is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
12. the person driving the boat is on the right of the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Hobby         | board-games | baking | sudoku    | magic-tricks  | puzzles    |
| Music-Genre   | classical    | house       | ambient      | jazz | funk        |
| Nationality   | indonesian   | nigerian     | british    | german  | canadian     |
| Transport     | ship    | boat | snowmobile | airplane | jet-ski |

