.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: skydiving, board-games, camping, photography, traveling
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: animation, sports, disaster, romance, fantasy
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: funk, folk, country, rock, trance
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: rugby, ice-hockey, climbing, biathlon, skateboarding
 1. the person who's hobby is traveling is the fan of folk##1
 2. the person who's sport is biathlon is in the middle##1
 3. the fan of rock is in the middle##1
 4. the person watching animation movies is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 6. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the fan of funk##1
 7. the fan of trance is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 8. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
 9. the fan of country is on the far left##1
10. the person who's sport is rugby is the person watching romance movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
12. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the fan of trance##1
13. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the person watching fantasy movies and the person who's hobby is camping##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | skydiving | traveling     | camping   | board-games   | photography |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy  | sports | animation | romance | disaster        |
| Music-Genre   | country      | folk      | rock       | trance       | funk       |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | skateboarding  | biathlon    | rugby    | climbing        |

