.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-4::.
There 5 different types of food: carrot, blueberry, strawberry, banana, grapefruit
The people have 5 different hobbies: video-games, camping, writing, filmmaking, gardening
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: gospel, metal, house, d&b, ambient
There are 5 different nationalities: french, italian, argentine, german, malaysian
 1. the italian is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the fan of metal##1
 3. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
 4. the malaysian is between the fan of d&b and the person eating banana##2
 5. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 6. the fan of ambient is on the right of the argentine##1
 7. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
 8. the person who's hobby is gardening is the fan of metal##1
 9. the fan of ambient is in the middle##1
10. the fan of d&b is the french##1
11. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
12. the french is on the right of the fan of house##1
13. the fan of metal is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| Food          | grapefruit  | strawberry     | banana   | blueberry     | carrot |
| Hobby         | gardening | video-games    | writing  | filmmaking | camping   |
| Music-Genre   | metal        | gospel    | ambient     | house     | d&b    |
| Nationality   | italian    | argentine | german | malaysian | french   |

