.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-5::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, soy-milk, coffee, sprite
There 5 different types of food: zucchini, cauliflower, strawberry, spinach, tomato
The people have 5 different jobs:  firefighter, freelancer, journalist, engineer, entrepreneur
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: rowing, swimming, lacrosse, ice-hockey, sailing
 1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the firefighter##1
 2. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 3. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 4. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person eating zucchini##2
 5. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
 7. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the freelancer##1
 8. the entrepreneur is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 9. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the firefighter##1
11. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
12. the engineer is on the left of the firefighter##1
13. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
| Beverage   | coffee       | sprite       | cola   | soy-milk      | iced-tea    |
| Food       | tomato | spinach        | zucchini       | strawberry       | cauliflower |
| Job        | entrepreneur     | freelancer        | engineer | firefighter        | journalist  |
| Sport      | ice-hockey | lacrosse | rowing      | sailing | swimming  |

