 8. the indian is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the brazilian##1
10. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far right##1
11. the person watching romance movies is between the person watching spy movies and the person who's sport is biathlon##2
12. the person drinking milk is on the right of the mexican##1
13. the person watching spy movies is on the far left##1

