 7. the canadian is on the right of the american##1
 8. the spanish is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the rabbit is the canadian##1
10. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
11. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the american##1
12. the owner of the fish is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
13. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
