 9. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
10. the person driving the motorbike is the person drinking fanta##1
11. the owner of the guinea-pig is the pilot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2      |     3      |       4       |     5     |
