 3. the person drinking cola is the person who's hobby is singing##1
 4. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 5. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
 6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
 7. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 8. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 9. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
10. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far left##1
11. the person driving the roller is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
12. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
13. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage    | water       | coffee    | hot-chocolate | cola  | tea        |
| Hobby       | chess | magic-tricks | collecting  | singing | camping    |
| Sport       | weightlifting        | water-polo   | ice-hockey  | tennis   | biathlon |
| Transport   | subway       | roller      | skateboard      | bike | boat  |

