.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: water, lemonade, coffee, hot-chocolate, fanta
The people have 5 different jobs:  dancer, manager, paramedic, lawyer, mechanic
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: superhero, time-travel, comedy, sports, epic
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: pop, metal, disco, dubstep, funk
