 2. the lawyer is between the person watching comedy movies and the paramedic##2
 3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the lawyer##1
 4. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
 5. the person watching superhero movies is in the middle##1
 6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the mechanic and the fan of metal##2
 7. the fan of dubstep is the person drinking coffee##1
 8. the person drinking water is the fan of disco##1
 9. the fan of pop is on the left of the mechanic##1
10. the dancer is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
11. the paramedic is the person watching time-travel movies##1
