The people prefer 5 different music-genres: pop, disco, folk, house, indie
There are 5 different nationalities: french, dutch, pakistani, british, nigerian
 1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
 2. the person watching action movies is between the british and the fan of indie##2
 3. the fan of indie is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 4. the person watching action movies is the fan of pop##1
 5. the fan of pop is between the nigerian and the fan of folk##2
 6. the nigerian is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 7. the person watching western movies is the fan of house##1
 8. the person who's hobby is indie-climbing is the fan of disco##1
 9. the french is the fan of disco##1
10. the person who's hobby is indie-climbing is on the right of the pakistani##1
11. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
12. the person watching epic movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
